  "texts": [
    "The proof follows exactly the same lines as that of Theorem 2.5 in [CGV25] to the difference that we build upon Proposition 3.2 instead of Proposition2.4 in [CGV25].",
    "We skip the details.",
    "Corollary 3.4.",
    "Let q = n -1/r for some r = γ + α/β where γ, α, and β are positive integers with α < β.",
    "Consider the blow-up graph with fasteners G κ,γ,a with κ = 2βγ and a = α/β."
